  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This exquisite blade is a Long sword +2: Dragonslayer (Peridan).  Few dare to create such items as this, for who does not fear the wrath of dragons, and what action would more tempt their reckoning? Yet, at a time lost in Faerun's past, there was a need, and this sword was forged in answer. \n\nTempered by a wizard's skill, this blade protects the wielder from the fear they should rightly feel while staring down a dragon's maw. It also bolsters with regeneration, dispels the trickery of illusions, and dares to do double damage against the greatest creatures of the Realms."
    }
